{
  "stem": "33.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "They-- each blamed, you know, each other for what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The religious Jews would say, sure.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "God is punishing us because you guys turned away from God, and you think you're not Jews anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And of course, our side would say, sure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Because you look different, you act different, you don't-- you're not integrated within your community.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "That's why bad things happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And you know, we found out that nobody was right, because it was enough if you had one Jewish grandparent.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I mean, you could have been born Catholic, or Protestant, the laws, most of the laws, they'd apply to you.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "My parents were really different types.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "My father was very low key, even though he was a businessman-- and a successful one.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But as-- I always thought that he would be happier being maybe a writer or a poet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He loved the theater.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "He loved to read.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "He loved music.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "But he was, I think, down to earth enough to know that one needs money to be happy in life.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "He was very different from his generation of Jewish businessmen because of the fact that money was never a goal in his eyes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Money was just something that assured a good life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "But he was never a slave of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And I guess the only consolation when I think of him being dead so young was that he did have a good life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "He never denied us or himself anything that he could afford to have or to give us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "My mother was very outgoing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "She had a wonderful sense of humor.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "When my friends came to our house, she really used to keep us in stitches with her stories.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And she was very funny.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "She loved people.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
